---
title: Smokey Eggplant & Chicken Couscous Salad with Flaked Almonds & Mint Yoghurt Dressing
description: Tonight’s salad is hearty and flavourful, with fluffy couscous, chicken, roasted eggplant and fresh veggies all tossed together. We’ll mix up a mint yoghurt dressing as well for extra pizzazz - drizzle it all over for an extra touch of creamy tartness and sprinkle over some almonds for that much-needed crunch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
